iconsmaker (0.1.1-1~ppa3) noble; urgency=medium

  * Point cargo at the vendored sources with an absolute path
    ($(CURDIR)/vendor). The relative "vendor" was resolved by cargo relative to
    CARGO_HOME, not the package root, so the offline build failed with
    "failed to read root of directory source: .../debian/vendor".

 -- Matt Comeione <oss@ideocentric.com>  Sat, 04 Jul 2026 18:00:00 +0000

iconsmaker (0.1.1-1~ppa2) noble; urgency=medium

  * Build against the versioned Rust 1.85 toolchain (cargo-1.85/rustc-1.85)
    instead of the archive default. Ubuntu's unversioned rustc lags upstream
    (noble ships 1.75); edition 2024 requires rustc >= 1.85, so the previous
    "rustc (>= 1.85)" Build-Depends was unsatisfiable on noble.

 -- Matt Comeione <oss@ideocentric.com>  Sat, 04 Jul 2026 13:00:00 +0000

